on reading compounds: 猪口【チョコ】sake cup, small deep porcelain bowl for serving food
猪牙舟【チョキブネ】long, thin, roofless small boat (used as a river taxi during the Edo period)
玄猪【ゲンチョ】day of the boar in the tenth month, mochi eaten on the day of the boar (esp. at the time of the boar)
kun reading compounds: 猪【い】hog (esp. a wild boar, but also including the domesticated pig)
猪年【いのししどし】year of the boar
鹿猪【しかいのしし】babirusa (Babyrousa babyrussa)
